value.0: Devout worshipers of evil, pureblooded Yuan-ti often appear human at first glance. It is only when they draw close that their snake-like features can be seen. However, this particular one looks well armored and armed, not at all friendly, and determined to put up a real fight.
Strange runes and pictographs, likely arcane in nature, have been scorched into the sides of this hide-covered strongbox.
